{"data": [{"id": "4743461", "title": "CS Disco: Same Old Blues - Reiterate Sell", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Saxophone with musical notes\" data-id=\"148121657\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RapidEye/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction and investment thesis</strong></h2> <p>CS Disco (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LAW\" title=\"CS Disco, Inc.\">LAW</a></span>) continued its struggles in Q3, posting close to stagnating revenues for the 4<sup>th</sup> consecutive quarter. The legal tech company, trying to reshape the law industry with its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148121657/image_148121657.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743461-cs-disco-stock-profitability-continues-to-be-impacted-reiterate-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 06:59:42"}, {"id": "4743460", "title": "SUSA: A More Aggressive ESG Fund With Disappointing Growth And Quality Features", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Group of business ESG meeting environment, society and governance, discussing renewable energy wind turbine solar panel, eco- friendly net zero emission business ethical, reduce carbon footprint pollution greenhouse gas reuse recycle for sustainable\" data-id=\"2054522581\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1027px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Happy Kikky</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p><span>According to its </span><a href=\"https://www.ishares.com/us/literature/fact-sheet/susa-ishares-msci-usa-esg-select-etf-fund-fact-sheet-en-us.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.ishares.com/us/literature/fact-sheet/susa-ishares-msci-usa-esg-select-etf-fund-fact-sheet-en-us.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span>fact sheet</span></a><span>, the iShares MSCI USA ESG Select ETF (</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SUSA\" title=\"iShares MSCI USA ESG Select ETF\">SUSA</a></span><span>) seeks to provide investors with exposure to large- and mid-cap U.S. stocks with leading environmental, social, and governance practices. It also avoids companies with low ESG ratings and</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054522581/image_2054522581.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743460-susa-more-aggressive-esg-fund-disappointing-growth-quality-features", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 06:45:18"}, {"id": "4743458", "title": "Braze: Remain Optimistic On The Growth Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scroll Hole\" data-id=\"1477194614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1097px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment overview</h2> <p>I wrote about <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4719776-braze-inc-growth-strength-remain-healthy\">Braze, Inc.</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRZE\" title=\"Braze, Inc.\">BRZE</a></span>) previously (September 2024) with a buy rating, as I saw the fallen share price as an attractive entry point and that any form of slowdown in operating performance should see</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477194614/image_1477194614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743458-braze-stock-q3-earnings-remain-optimistic-on-growth-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 06:18:19"}, {"id": "4743455", "title": "Amid Macroeconomic Headwinds, I'm Bearish On Dollar General", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar General Retail Location. Dollar General is a Small-Box Discount Retailer I\" data-id=\"1139364763\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The U.S. retail landscape has evolved a lot in the last few years. With the effects of the pandemic lingering, many are still to fully recover from uncertain supply chains, volatile demand, and rampant inflation. To me, no company represents this challenge better than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139364763/image_1139364763.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743455-amid-macroeconomic-headwinds-bearish-on-dollar-general-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 05:57:24"}, {"id": "4743453", "title": "Tracking Ole Andreas Halvorsen's Viking Global Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tiger cub (Panthera tigris) against white background\" data-id=\"200502280-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Harvey/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Ole Andreas Halvorsen's 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Viking Global's regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1103804/000110380424000006/0001103804-24-000006-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200502280/image_200502280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743453-ole-andreas-halvorsen-viking-global-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 05:20:02"}, {"id": "4743449", "title": "SkyWest: Likely Overvalued As Air Travel Demand Growth Slows", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Alaska Airlines Embraer ERJ aircraft operated by SkyWest Airlines, landing at the airport at dusk.\" data-id=\"2136657013\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jon Tetzlaff/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JETS\" title=\"ETF Series Solutions - U.S. Global Jets ETF\">JETS</a>) shows that the airline industry is among the few that failed to recover after the 2020 crash. The first half of 2024 was challenging and saw drawdowns in most major airline stocks; however, the industry has rallied in recent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2136657013/image_2136657013.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743449-skywest-stock-likely-overvalued-as-air-travel-demand-growth-slows", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 04:33:13"}, {"id": "4743448", "title": "G-III Apparel Group Continues To Perform, But I Think It Has Reached Fair Value", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"gran tienda minorista de ropa DKNY\" data-id=\"2150222584\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Robert Way/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>G-III Apparel Group (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GIII\" title=\"G-III Apparel Group, Ltd.\">GIII</a></span>) reported positive and in-line 3Q25 results, derisking the company's largest quarter of the year. Sales were flat compared to last year, but its own brands grew as much as 30% YoY, mainly via door expansion. Q3 included shipments related to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150222584/image_2150222584.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743448-g-iii-apparel-group-stock-continues-perform-reached-fair-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 04:14:02"}, {"id": "4743451", "title": "Stitch Fix, Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Stitch Fix, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106102\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743451-stitch-fix-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 03:48:47"}, {"id": "4743442", "title": "Vail Resorts: Shares Are Worth Considering On Better Results, Higher Guidance", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1661732562/image_1661732562.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A couple cross country skiing on a beautiful winter day.\" data-id=\"1661732562\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/16617325